source.name: GOES Composite - Central U.S. Imagery
source.description: This product includes 10 km, remapped GOES-East/West composited images in infrared, visible, shortwave infrared and water vapor imagery and loops. The following infrared enhancements are also available: AVN, Dvorak, JSL, RGB, Funktop, and Rainbow. This product is generated every 30 Minutes.
